status: MARC21-007: Color characteristics of a videorecording

definition (en): Executed in more than one color.
Work or collection is a combination of black-and-white, colored, and/or other images.

scope note (en): E.g., a videorecording with sound only.

definition (en): Color characteristics of an item are not known.
Color other than one color, black-and-white, multicolored, mixed.
